  "title": "Planning Manager (HDB/Condo/Landed Projects)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Develop project schedules, monitor progress, and implement corrective actions when necessary.</li><li>Coordinate with project managers and site teams to ensure timely delivery.</li><li>Analyze project data to optimize scheduling and resource allocation.</li><li>Conduct resource planning and risk assessment for projects.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>At least 5 years’ experience in planning for <strong>HDB, Condo, and Landed projects.</strong></li><li>Experience in coordinating with multiple projects simultaneously.</li><li>Proficient in <strong>MS Project or Primavera P6.</strong></li><li>Strong analytical and organizational skills.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><ul><li>Registration: R1326740</li></ul>",
